		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="426" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火斧从地里挖出火史莱姆，给斧子上<span textDecoration="underline">火附魔</span><span>后丢出，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">37.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，火斧拿着斧子跳起来下落，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。若斧子附带</span><span color="#ff9900">火附魔</span><span>，则在前方扇形区产生5道火喷，每道造成</span><span color="#ff9999">16.5%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ff3f00">强攻强化：</span><span>落地时周围产生7道火喷。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/火斧丘丘暴徒.assets/Image_13.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/火斧丘丘暴徒.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1393" y="425">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="432" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火斧进行至多2段的2种普通攻击：<br/><span color="#99ffb2">旋-劈</span><span>、</span><span color="#99ffb2">旋-旋</span><span>，每段攻击均造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span>伤害，其中下劈攻击将在前方产生一道3段的火喷，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">16.5%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ff3f00">强攻强化：</span><span>下劈攻击时产生3道火喷。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="511" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当火斧的斧子存在附魔，而玩家又距离比较远时，火斧从地里挖出火史莱姆丢出，造成<span color="#ff9999">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="434" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">火斧横拿斧子转圈圈，触碰造成<span color="#b9b9b9">12.5%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ff9999">12.5%</span><span>伤害，持续3s，旋转结束后施放尾刀，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
